    <h2>{`Medianizer`}</h2>
    <Indent pad={2} mdxType="Indent">
      <p>{`A Medianizer is a type of smart-contract in the Maker Protocolâ€™s Oracle system that collects price-data from Feeds and calculates a reference price by calculating a median.`}</p>
